{"article_id":"XAeQVJ2jzC8kS1LP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Aaron Carroll :","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Obamacare rollout has been a disaster ;","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"there 's no excuse for it","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"He says","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"problems at front end of process make it hard to get even through first step","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"He says","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"insurance firms getting garbled date ;","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"administration calling in IT experts","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Carroll :","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Obamacare needed ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"but these first days have created problems political and real","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"The rollout of the federal Obamacare website has been a disaster , full stop .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"There can be no excuses ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"nor will I be making any .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"It 's been clear for years what needed to be done ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and failing was not an option .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The exchanges , and the website","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that allowed access to them ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"had to work ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and they just do not .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"I wrote a week or two ago","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that the initial problems with the HealthCare.gov website appeared to be because of volume issues .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"That could be spun as either a positive or negative thing .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"But it now seems that the surge was not the cause of the malfunctions .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"After the first weekend ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"when the administration added additional capacity to the servers ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"the issues did n't go away .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"What are they ?","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"I wish","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"I could say for sure .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"But some good reports have come out","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that detail just a few of the problems .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"The first appears to be that the administration decided","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that people would need to provide a significant amount of personal detail","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"to look at coverage options .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"I can attest to this first-hand .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"I have insurance through my work ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"so I do n't need exchange coverage ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"but I was still interested in looking at what was available .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"I had to provide a lot of information , about my job and family ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"before I could do so .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"It 's possible that this was because administrators wanted to be able to provide subsidy information to people with the premium costs ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"so as to soften the blow","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"of how expensive insurance could be ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"but no one knows for sure .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Regardless , this complicated things significantly .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Sullivan :","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Obama should have apologized","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"MUST WATCH Sullivan :","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Obama should have apologized","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"07:26","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Mystery surrounds the 'Obamacare Girl '","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"MUST WATCH Mystery surrounds the 'Obamacare Girl '","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"02:25","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"But that 's just the front end .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"The back end is also a real problem .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Insurance companies are reporting","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that the data","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"they are receiving from the HealthCare.gov website","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"is garbled .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"This means that automatic processing of the insurance plans","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"being ordered","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"is impossible .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Oddly enough , the problems on the front end are actually helping here .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"So few orders are actually making it through","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that insurance companies are able to sort through the bad data by hand","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"to complete enrollment .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"if things improve on the front end ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"then there 's no way","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"these companies can do millions of applications","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"without good data .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"The administration is bragging","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that upwards of half a million applications have started .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Shockingly few of them have been completed , though .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"The front end has a number of steps ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"including submitting your information ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"assessing for eligibility","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"and then shopping for insurance .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"The number","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"being cited by the administration","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"refers only to people","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"who have completed the first step .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"There are people","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"who believe","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"that government can never do things as well as the private sector .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"I 'm not one of those people .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"But in this specific instance , those people have a point .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"JUST WATCHED Obama :","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"No sugarcoating website issues","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"MUST WATCH Obama : No sugarcoating website issues","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"03:18","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"JUST WATCHED Obama details website workarounds","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"MUST WATCH Obama details website workarounds","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"02:49","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Evidently , those in charge of the rollout of the exchange website were unprepared .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"They did n't have the necessary experience","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to manage the more than 50 different contractors","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"producing software independently","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"that would eventually need to function together as a whole .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"This is incredibly technical work ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"and it 's not clear that government was in a good position","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"to direct things here .","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"It appears that the Obama administration has learned its lesson .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"Administration officials are now calling in `` more computer experts ''","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"to try and fix the problem .","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"But this may be too little , too late .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"Some are saying","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"that","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"even if the administration pours in massive resources ,","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"the problems may not be fixed by December 15 , the deadline","depth":17},{"id":118,"text":"for when insurance needs to be bought","depth":18},{"id":119,"text":"for it to be covering people on January 1 .","depth":18},{"id":120,"text":"Even if the administration can get this done within a month ,","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"some in the insurance industry are concerned","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"that these issues may act as a filter","depth":17},{"id":123,"text":"to dissuade healthy people from getting insurance .","depth":17},{"id":124,"text":"If it 's really , really hard to complete an application ,","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"then only truly ill people may have the perseverance","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"to do so .","depth":17},{"id":127,"text":"That could lead to problems in the pool of people","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"signing up for insurance .","depth":16},{"id":129,"text":"The administration needs healthy people to buy insurance , too ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"for the exchanges to function optimally","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"If we were talking about a company having mismanaged things so badly ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"you could be sure","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that heads would roll .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Many would be fired ,","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"and there would be a change in management .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"But that may not be possible here .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Were Health and Human Services Secretary Kathleen Sebelius to go ,","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"President Barack Obama could n't get someone else vetted and through the Senate nomination process in an expedient manner .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"He 's likely stuck with his current team , or no team at all .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"That does n't mean Obamacare will fail .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"It 's still possible that this could all be fixed .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"It 's also possible that","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"should significant issues continue ,","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"timelines might be adjusted","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"to accommodate implementation issues .","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"But these will cause problems political and real in nature .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"Continued failures in the exchange rollout give the President 's opponents fuel","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"to attack him and his health care reform .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"More importantly , they prevent people","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"who really do need insurance , and the care","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"it allows ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"from getting what they need .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":305,"left":0,"right":304,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":198,"right":303,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":163,"right":197,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":160,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":155,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":1,"right":154,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":156,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":157,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":162,"left":9,"right":161,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":171,"right":196,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":167,"right":170,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":165,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":12,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"